Enable STP on a Switch
Switch(config)# spanning-tree vlan <VLAN-ID>
Check STP Status
Switch# show spanning-tree
Switch# show spanning-tree vlan <VLAN-ID>
Switch# show spanning-tree interface <interface-id>
Configure Root Bridge Priority
Switch(config)# spanning-tree vlan <VLAN-ID> priority <value>
Configure PortFast (For Access Ports)
Switch(config-if)# spanning-tree portfast
Configure BPDU Guard (Protect Against Loops)
Switch(config-if)# spanning-tree bpduguard enable
Rapid STP (RSTP)
Switch(config)# spanning-tree mode rapid-pvst
